30:01.325 --> 30:02.493
Well, we're trying.

30:02.493 --> 30:03.786
- Yeah. Yeah.
- Yeah.

30:03.786 --> 30:07.456
Well, that's wonderful.
Isn't that wonderful?

30:07.456 --> 30:09.083
It's wonderful. Yeah.

30:10.459 --> 30:11.627
Yeah.

30:15.714 --> 30:19.260
Candy, I heard about you
