30:19.260 --> 30:21.262
are talking about a

30:22.638 --> 30:25.975
rediscovering yourself.
A kind of a "rediscover you."

30:25.975 --> 30:28.060
- Wait, did I hear that correctly?
- Yes, you did.

30:28.060 --> 30:29.645
