30:32.398 --> 30:33.482
Home improvement.

30:36.944 --> 30:39.863
And then, I'm still taking
my writers' workshop classes.

30:40.656 --> 30:43.200
I'm actually moving on
to an advanced level.

30:43.200 --> 30:44.451
That's wonderful.

30:47.663 --> 30:48.831
