35:20.394 --> 35:21.353
So

35:22.855 --> 35:27.985
I found a love letter
from Allan Gore to Candy.

35:28.902 --> 35:32.865
I was looking for a letter
she'd written me just after we married

35:32.865 --> 35:36.076
