35:37.911 --> 35:40.372
I need to know something.
I know she would tell you.

35:42.207 --> 35:43.250
Is it over?

35:45.335 --> 35:47.963
- Pat--
- Is it over?

35:54.595 --> 35:55.888
It is.

35:56.972 --> 35:58.348
And it won't happen again.

35:59.391 --> 36:01.310
It was just a brief thing and, honestly,

36:01.310 --> 36:03.312
it was more friendship than anything.

36:04.354 --> 36:06.356
It was just a stage
that Candy went through.

36:06.356 --> 36:08.233
